40|$|AbstractEvery nonassociative Boolean domain can be {{embedded}} into a Boolean quasifield. A {{similar result}} holds for medial nonassociative Boolean domains. We describe connections between medial nonassociative <b>Boolean</b> <b>rings</b> and associative rings in which squaring is an automorphism. The lattice of varieties of such associative rings and the lattice of varieties of medial nonassociative <b>Boolean</b> <b>rings</b> are isomorphic {{to the one}} point completion of the lattice of finite factor closed sets of positive integers. We describe the free members of such varieties...|$|R
